'''''Hammer''''' was an [[IPV-1 System Patrol Craft]] belonging to the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire]]. It was stationed at [[Quesna Base]] for guard duty when [[Ace Azzameen/Legends|Ace Azzameen]], along with [[Dunari]], came to rescue his brother [[Emon Azzameen|Emon]], who was imprisoned there at the time. They delivered a container of [[Tibanna/Legends|tibanna]], which had been booby trapped, and it provided cover for Dunari as he boarded the station and rescued Emon. The ''Hammer'', along with all the [[TIE/ln space superiority starfighter/Legends|TIE/LN starfighters]] and [[Alpha-class Xg-1 Star Wing/Legends|Assault Gunboats]] present, were destroyed in the ensuing chaos.<ref name="X-Wing">''[[Star Wars: X-Wing Alliance]]''</ref>

